"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**As Metalink continues to grow, we want to keep it the safe and zen-like space you have come to know. 🧘🏻‍♂️**\\n\\nIt’s why we’re committed to rolling out features that protect our users against the spam and scams so rampant on existing platforms. 😤\\n\\nThere are three initial ways we’re accomplishing this: \\n\\n**1. We’re currently the only place on the internet where you can chat and see someone’s NFT holdings at the same time.** 💎\\n\\nThis makes it more difficult for scammers to create fake accounts and impersonate others. \\n\\nIf ever in doubt, simply click on the user’s profile and see all their holdings verified on the blockchain.\\n\\n**2. There are no passwords on Metalink. In fact, your account isn’t even tied to an email address. Welcome to the future authentication standard.** 🔐\\n\\n> ***“81% of hacking-related breaches used stolen passwords and/or weak passwords.” -Cloudnine***\\n\\n**3.  Today, we’re adding an additional layer of protection to Metalink with Message Request Inboxes.** 📬\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/H5mY8J3zB7oLBovSFfyGR.jpeg?height=744&width=1406)\\n\\nStarting today, all messages from new users will pass through a Message Request inbox before entering your primary inbox. \\n\\nYou’ll be able to see who requested and quickly verify what NFTs they hold before deciding to engage with them. \\n\\nWe all know the NFT space is rife with scams. It doesn’t take long for your space to be flooded with messages you don’t want, from people you don’t know on existing platforms.\\n\\nThere’s an opportunity to create a new kind of digital space that’s safer, more secure, and scam-resistant than the status quo. \\n\\nOur mission is to empower users to completely own their connected experiences… From social to payments and everything in between. 💫\\n\\nBut that all starts with creating a safe space where our community can feel at ease interacting and transacting in a permission-less future. 🤝🔮\\n\\nToday is one small step in that direction. \\n\\nStay tuned for what comes next…\\n\\n \\n \",\"timestamp\":1639867501,\"title\":\"🎁🎄 Day 3 of 12 Days of Metalink - Message Request Inboxes 🎁🎄\"},\"digest\":\"JJ2hKJGHIHT_NEXi4EngWdfmy8vfgqT5jBmgmrV6G5c\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf63e4D72b7f296aE94254a10be56896A19D4FfbE\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qp6lQJY1y6T0WtomxotZKlL2rhnOqKxwtluKUZB8GWk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"H0wuxYrPErnT7r3-un9hgAHt15Ie9ewA5zsJ1EJR_fY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"OwtojywopDlxMi5Pc2_Ke0-66eEKcsqw1MhciXgDJ0izBTH9Ab9rXDky-0cuboLum1YUUvUU7jLloNPgNFKAdQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0c9ecd2a8137435a6b96212191a51805965d27ae0e1c4026916a026e2b115f9c357549e028e55965998a132f206b4b524159202c5141c60e9343e39c459d5c8c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qp6lQJY1y6T0WtomxotZKlL2rhnOqKxwtluKUZB8GWk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"H0wuxYrPErnT7r3-un9hgAHt15Ie9ewA5zsJ1EJR_fY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"_gxK3cf--XM2oyxtKYQpmEeTf3c_VGGDoBUFndftkss\"}"